name: Blue knit littlefee dress
description:
Hat, socks and dress, 1920s flavor.

crochet cloche, hand knit dress and socks. Super soft Merino, with non metallic snap in the back.

fits littlefee, Yo, Lati Green, and similar sized ball jointed dolls

shoes, wig and doll not included.

My model is a Fairyland Littlefee "Elf El".

I knit and sew for several doll sizes, and will do custom work. 
you can see more of my work over on flickr (same user name).

name: Pink knit pukipuki, lati white, felix sized dress
description:
Pukipuki, Lati White, felix Brownie size sweet pink merino dress with white alpaca trim and black ribbon belt & matching cloche hat.

Hand knit with crochet trim.
snap closure for ease of dressing.

cloche hat is big enough to fit nicely over wig.

this listing is ONLY for the dress and the hat.

model is a Fairyland Pukipuki choco Sugar

I knit and sew for several doll sizes, and will do custom work. 
you can see more of my work over on flickr (same user name).

name: Impressionists Garden Bunny
description:
3 in tall crochet bunny, in spring color speckles that remind me of an Impressionistic painting.

He matches the doll dresses in the "Impressionist's Garden" yarn. This is a hand dyed yarn so this bunny is one of a kind.

He's perky with his sweet silk tail.

Shown here with a doll house couch that is 1/12 scale, at 3in tall he's smaller than a Pukipuki doll, and would make a great companion for any sized ball jointed doll, or a lovely inhabitant for a doll house.

I'm always happy to do custom work, you can see more of my work over on flickr.com (under the same username).  If you've seen my work elsewhere or at scifi conventions and the piece is not shown here, please send me a note. I may have that piece or something similar in stock.  Or I can make something similar to fit your request.

name: Hello Kthulhu in a green dress
description:
So cute you don't mind going insane or having your soul ripped out for devouring.

She'd be an excellent companion for any size Ball Jointed Doll... as a huggy for the SD, MSD, Yo-SD, and a super big plushie (imaginary friend?) for a Tiny!

Hello Kthulhu Extra large (6in tall)
in a spring green dress.

Huggable elder god,
6 in tall green dress in wool!
She has sweet black eyes, 4 face tentacles, jointed arms and legs as well as wings.

Intoxicatingly Kawaii!
